imdb.plot outline: This show follows the adventures of two halo toys' lives. One is a dimwitted Halo 2 Master Chief action figure and the other is a brilliant and skilled video game player who is a Halo 2 Arbiter action figure. They go from battling hackers to battling each other during their wacky mishaps. Watch and enjoy this universally, critically acclaimed show that has swept the nation.
imdb.title: Arby 'n' the Chief
plot: This show follows the adventures of two halo toys' lives. One is a dimwitted Halo 2 Master Chief action figure and the other is a brilliant and skilled video game player who is a Halo 2 Arbiter action figure. They go from battling hackers to battling each other during their wacky mishaps. Watch and enjoy this universally, critically acclaimed show that has swept the nation.::Anonymous

Season 1 The Arbiter and Master Chief form an unlikely bond and explore the world of video games and the world wide Web, encountering all kinds of characters and situations. Season 2 The duo are back to their usual misadventures in the second season of the hit Web series/machinima. The two figures deal with new map packs, new problems and new friends. Season 3 Master Chief and Arbiter's antics continue online, this time faced with MLG players, hackers, companies, glitches and more! Season 4 Excited with the upcoming release of Halo Reach, the figures find themselves in a whole new slew of situations. Fighting gaming addicts, running from spiders and even answering fan mail. Season 5 When an old love interest of Arbiter gets engaged for a Halo wedding, things start to change for the two Halo toys. Explosive ceremonies, hard hitting vows and one hell of a do. Season 6 Xbox live is under threat by a malicious hacker group who are hell bent on destruction... who can save the day? Only Master Chief and his trusty companion the Arbiter. Season 7 With the apartment filling up, tensions rise between Chief and the other residents. A horrible accident and a dark secret forces Arbiter and Chief to seek company in a troll hacker gang. Season 8 Reeling from the effects of the previous season, both toys awaken to see the world has changed around them, and the games as well. Both of them must work together to find their purpose in life. In L.A. The toys relocate to California to live with Claire. Bored with their surroundings, both toys venture out into the world to find out they're not so different after all. The movie A bet between the Master Chief and Arbiter goes awry and Chief must embark on a journey that will test his friendship with Arbiter and change his life forever. Endgame A master hacker/drug dealer is chased to Canada by a Russian operative. Arbiter finds love in an unlikely place. The toys decide to save the day one last time
